; 2-bit counter constrained to values 0 and 1
; Without constraint, counter reaches 3 (bad). With constraint, safe.
1 sort bitvec 2
2 sort bitvec 1
3 zero 1
4 one 1
5 state 1 cnt
6 init 1 5 3
7 add 1 5 4
8 next 1 5 7
; constraint: cnt < 2
9 constd 1 2
10 ult 2 5 9
11 constraint 10
; bad: cnt == 3
12 constd 1 3
13 eq 2 5 12
14 bad 13
